Is it possible to scope the work using a definition of 6LoWPAN rather 
than the definitions in the LWIG draft?  Adrian holds a DISCUSS on the 
LWIG draft because of the scoping of those definitions.  He proposed 
that the 6lo charter avoid those definitions by scoping its work based 
on some 6LoWPAN description/definition.

Thoughts?  Proposed text?

Brian

